    {
      "content": "Even if an attacker manages to learn the user's password, it is useless without also having possession of the trusted device.",
      "pos": [
        4623,
        4748
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Should the user lose the device, the person who finds it won't be able to use it unless he or she also knows the user's password.",
