      "content": "If you do not have any of the above, then to begin using Azure Multi-Factor Authentication, you first need an Azure subscription or an <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Azure trial subscription<ept id=\"p1\">](http://azure.microsoft.com/pricing/free-trial/)</ept>."
